{"tid":585767,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Alexa 忽然自己笑嚇死人 Amazon 緊急修復","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T04:08:48.000Z","uid":1121,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90cda0e2a6af8b49c6a3c897ed921bb86c2bb712","tid":585767,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"智能喇叭在歐美大行其道，可以方便的用語音操作各種功能。不過如果在半夜忽然自己啟動然後發出笑聲，的確相當可怕。最近 Amazon Alexa 就出現了這樣的問題，需要緊急修復。<br />\n<br />\n今次受影響的不只是 Amazon 的 Echo 智能喇叭，其他配備 Alexa 的智能喇叭也同樣收到影響。有用家發現喇叭會忽然自己啟動，並且發出笑聲。無論是在日間還是晚上，如果聽到下面影片一樣的笑聲，肯定會被嚇到。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 方面在知道問題之後已經快速找出原因。據 Amazon 解釋，今次的問題原因是由於 Alexa 誤以為聽到「Alexa, laugh（Alexa，笑吧」的指令，於是就笑幾聲回應。Amazon 現在把觸發的指令改為「Alexa, can you laugh?（Alexa，你可以笑嗎？）」，而 Alexa 在笑之前也會先說一句「Sure, I can laugh.（當然，我會笑）」，即使遇到錯誤觸發的問題，也不會這麼兀突。Amazon 將會推出更新修正問題，避免之後 Alexa 變成鬼故的主角。<br />\n<br />\n來源：TNW"},{"pid":"174cd91723dd13e1434566d2bdfa509a1403733c","tid":585767,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/09/alexa-to-laugh-at-random/parts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2Falexa-to-laugh-at-random%2Fparts%2F&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=e3c3cf1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/09/alexa-to-laugh-at-random/parts/</a>"},{"pid":"ff9ac34efb1f27c22a6bb718216fd537df28d0b6","tid":585767,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20161031/large/1477894822_e56d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161031%2Flarge%2F1477894822_e56d.jpg&h=cc9dad8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d97f50aad4474156ce4942809807b1bf0b17862","tid":585767,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除